As of the 2010 Census, 108 people lived in Toad Hop. 107 residents were [[White American|White]] and 1 was of two or more races. The median age was 40 years old.<ref>{{cite web |title=U.S. Census website |url=https://www.census.gov |website=census.gov |publisher=United States Census Bureau |accessdate=January 26, 2020 }}</ref>

